{"type": "article", "id": 5381, "title": "Round-Frame Gold-Tone 太阳眼镜", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-20T07:29:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233810To1QDVlqw39fcMCB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自美国的设计师品牌 Thom Browne 日前发布了其最新系列的眼镜，其中一款 Round-Frame Gold-Tone 太阳眼镜，金丝制作的镜框搭配墨绿色的镜片，极具复古感。此外，设计师还为镜框两侧设置了用以抵挡侧面光线的网格罩，并给镜腿末端施以彩色细节用来点缀。全部手工艺皆由日本极富有经验的眼镜工匠完成。定价 1000 美元（约合人民币 6216 元），<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/en-us/mens/thom_browne/round-frame-gold-tone-sunglasses/525227\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233808xJ3YoQBVhMHmEAf1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233809rY4ZnailQufGO3Ik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052338095OMZgELVTKa4FoB6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}